MOST IMME
No.1/34/1/2012-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 30th October, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 30th October, 2012:
Smt. Panabaka Lakshmi relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Textiles and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas;
i.
Shri Milind Deora, the Minister of State in the Ministry of Communications and
Information Technology, also assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Shipping; and
ii.
ii.
Shri Lalchand Kataria relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Defence and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Rural Development.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members of the Planning
Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)
Joint Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy also forwarded for information to:
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Joint Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/ Additional Secretaries to the Govt.
of India/Chairman, Railway Board/Accounts Officer, Pay & Accounts Office, Cabinet Affairs, for
information.
(K.L. Sharma)
Joint Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the Govt. of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat
(Distribution Branch)/Rajya Sabha Secretariat (Distribution Branch)/ Establishment Officer,
Department of Personnel & Training/Ministry of External Affairs (Protocol Division)/Press
Information Bureau/Section Officer, NGO Section, Prime Minister's Office.
(K.L. Sharma)
